data.description: This Home is basically brand new. Constructed in 2020 with tons of upgrades and not to mentions a view a view a view! The home offers 3 nice large bedroom, beautiful fireplace, laundry, lots of storage, and 2 bath upstairs. From the dining room you go out onto a covered back deck with grilling area to enjoy the beautiful mountain views. Downstairs you have a huge den, office or 4th bedroom, full bath, and tons of storage.  This is a gorgeous home with tons to offer. Located in one of those subdivision that the kids can ride their bikes and enjoy the neighbors and  just mintures from the city limits.
